commit.message:
mips.md (sunlt_sf, [...]): Remove dependency on TARGET_DOUBLE_FLOAT.

2002-08-07  Chris Demetriou  <cgd@broadcom.com>

        * config/mips/mips.md (sunlt_sf, suneq_sf, sunle_sf): Remove
        dependency on TARGET_DOUBLE_FLOAT.

From-SVN: r56102

+2002-08-07  Chris Demetriou  <cgd@broadcom.com>
+
+	* config/mips/mips.md (sunlt_sf, suneq_sf, sunle_sf): Remove
+	dependency on TARGET_DOUBLE_FLOAT.
+
